## вњЁ Enhancements & Code Optimizations Made

1. **Performance & Caching ([predict.py](file:///c:/Users/98858/.gemini/antigravity/playground/golden-apollo/predict.py), [preprocess.py](file:///c:/Users/98858/.gemini/antigravity/playground/golden-apollo/preprocess.py))**:
   - Added `functools.lru_cache` to `lemmatizer.lemmatize` to speed up the preprocessing phase by memoizing duplicate word variants.
   - Added LRU caching wrapped around the predictive inference step to completely bypass computation on identical repeated headline evaluations.

2. **UI & User Experience Improvements ([index.html](file:///c:/Users/98858/.gemini/antigravity/playground/golden-apollo/templates/index.html), [style.css](file:///c:/Users/98858/.gemini/antigravity/playground/golden-apollo/static/style.css))**:
   - **Modernization**: Upgraded to a clean, highly modern dark-bordered "Enterprise" vibe. Added dynamic pulsating background gradients (`bg-gradient`) and custom Google typography (`Outfit` and `Playfair Display`).
   - **AJAX Single Page App**: Removed clumsy form redirects. The UI now fully relies on JavaScript `fetch()` calls to interact with the backend API, enabling smooth CSS state transitions (`expand-anim`) without page reloads.
   - **Interactive Elements**: Implemented an animating loading spinner SVG within the Analyze button, interactive typing character counters, and smooth probability bar fills.

3. **Error Handling & Architecture ([app.py](file:///c:/Users/98858/.gemini/antigravity/playground/golden-apollo/app.py))**:
   - Switched to strict JSON responses for all predictive routes (`/predict`).
   - Improved API resilience against empty inputs, and raised character-limit constraints dynamically.
   
4. **Keyword Extraction Nuance ([predict.py](file:///c:/Users/98858/.gemini/antigravity/playground/golden-apollo/predict.py))**:
   - Fixed TF-IDF weighting lookup logic to emphasize high-magnitude vector correlations matching the user's specific text string.

5. **Production Reliability ([wsgi.py](file:///c:/Users/98858/.gemini/antigravity/playground/golden-apollo/wsgi.py), [requirements.txt](file:///c:/Users/98858/.gemini/antigravity/playground/golden-apollo/requirements.txt))**:
   - Handled Windows terminal unicode emoji encode errors inside data ingestion scripts via `sys.stdout.reconfigure(encoding='utf-8')`.
   - Created [wsgi.py](file:///c:/Users/98858/.gemini/antigravity/playground/golden-apollo/wsgi.py) standard entry point and added `gunicorn` (Linux/Mac standard) and `waitress` (Windows standard) into [requirements.txt](file:///c:/Users/98858/.gemini/antigravity/playground/golden-apollo/requirements.txt) for highly scalable concurrency.

